      • MedRecord

        public MedRecord​(java.lang.String petInfo,
                 java.lang.String ownerInfo,
                 java.lang.String symptoms,
                 java.lang.String diagnosys,
                 java.lang.String status,
                 DateIn dateInn,
                 Pet sick)
        Constructor method for class MedRecord which is a medical record for the veterinary.
        Parameters:
        petInfo - The pet's information for the hospitalization. This param must not be empty.
        ownerInfo - The pet's owner information for the hospitalization. This param must not be empty.
        symptoms - The symptoms of the pet for the medical record.
        diagnosys - The diagnosys of the pet for the medical record.
        status - The status of the medical record. This param must not be empty.
        dateInn - The date (object) when the hospitalization started. This param must not be null.
        sick - The pet (object) in matter for the medical record. This param must not be null.

        public void addMeds​(java.util.ArrayList<ReqMed> petsMeds)
        When creating a new medical record, this method allows to add the prescribed medications to the medical record for the first time.

      • medRecordInfo

        public java.lang.String medRecordInfo()
        Information of a medical record such as pet's information, pet's owner information, dose, date when the hospitalization started and/or ended, symptoms of the pacient, diagnosys of the pacient, status of the hospitalization (open/closed), cost of the hospitalization and prescribed medication info is organized so it can be shown to the final user

        The information of a medical record in a format to be shown to the final user
